cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a real-world problem of recognizing parking signs using machine learning techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of active learning techniques and transfer learning approach to train the model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development of a machine learning solution to a real-world problem. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of crowd-sourcing tools to label the data. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the recognition of parking signs from street-level images, which can be considered as a multimedia data source.
